               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-919" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-919" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-919" type="surname" value="HAINES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-919" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>ELIZABETH HAINES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a widow. I keep a corn-chandler's shop in Clifton-street—I have known the prisoner some time—on the 14th of August, he came about eight o'clock at night, and asked for some hay—he walked across the shop, went to the parlour, took the watch out of the stand, and ran away—I stood at the door, and called, "Stop thief."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PHILIPS</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Had you known him long? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes: I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-920" type="witnessName">
